You need vertices
Lock this calling goroutine to its current operating system thread.
Initializes the GLFW library
Create Window and OpenGL context
Print any useful info/help.
Set callbacks for user input
Create and Use the Shader
Gen and Bind Vertex Array & Buffer
Copy vertices to array buffer
Get Uniform and Atrribute Locations
Do VertexAttribPointer & EnableVertexAttribArray
Set MVP as required
Set GL state for the draw. Clear, Culling, Depth etc
Main Draw Loop